 nerous help from our volunteer\, Tyler Stoner\, we welcome players of all
  ages and backgrounds to explore this fascinating game of territory\,&#16
 0\;tactics&#160\;and intuition. No experience is necessary\, just curiosi
 ty and willingness to learn!&#160\;&#160\;&#160\;  &#160\;All Indiana Uni
 versity events\, groups\, activities\, and&#160\;educational\, cultural\,
  and historical observances welcome all IU students and other members of 
 the Indiana University community.For more information\, view this event i
 n BeInvolved (https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11993421).
