 g\, cooking workshops—to introduce the aspects that Filipino culture ha
 s to offer.&#160\;Tagalog&#160\;na&#160\;Tayo! is open to everyone\, whet
 her&#160\;you're&#160\;a beginner\, fluent speaker\, or simply curious ab
